@node BALDU "Balduvian Trading Post"

@{b}Balduvian Trading Post@{ub}

Rarity  = AI(R2)
Type    = Land
Artist  = Tom Wanerstrand

Text(AI): When Balduvian Trading Post comes into play, sacrifice
          an untapped mountain or bury Balduvian Trading Post.
          <T>: Add <1R> to your mana pool.
          <1T>: Balduvian Trading Post deals 1 damage to target
          attacking creature.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_B.guide/BALDU}

