@node SHELT "Sheltered Valley"

@{b}Sheltered Valley@{ub}

Rarity  = AI(R2)
Type    = Land
Artist  = Rob Alexander

Text(AI): When Sheltered Valley comes into play, bury any other Sheltered
          Valley you control. During your upkeep, if you control three or
          fewer lands, gain 1 life.
          <T>: Add one colorless mana to your mana pool.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_S.guide/SHELT}

