Rarity  = AI(R2)
Type    = Land
Artist  = Liz Danforth

Text(AI): When Soldevi Excavations comes into play, sacrifice
          an untapped island or bury Soldevi Excavations.
          <T>: Add <1U> to your mana pool.
          <1T>: Look at the top card of your library. You may
          put that card on the bottom of your library.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_S.guide/SOLEX}

