@node THAWI "Thawing Glaciers"

@{b}Thawing Glaciers@{ub}

Rarity  = AI(R2)
Type    = Land
Artist  = Jeff A. Menges

Text(AI): Comes into play tapped.
          <1T>: Search your library for a basic land and put it into
          play tapped. This does not count towards your one land per
          turn limit. Shuffle your library afterwards. At the end of
          turn, return Thawing Glaciers to owner's hand.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_T.guide/THAGL}

